Hello Everyone (any Agadmator fans here ?)
I am a student pursuing my Bachelors in Computer Engineering. I am interested in Machine Learning and Deep Learning models and algorithms and now want to start contributing to Julia. I came across Julia a few months back and wanted to be a part of the community and want to learn about how to contribute to this fast growing language.
